Musician and businessman Akon is back in the studio. This time, he's working with rapper Tekashi 6ix9ine. They are working on a remix for Akon's 2003 hit single Locked Up. A video of them in studio working on the song trended on Twitter and people weren't happy. Most people said Akon was going to mess the song up if he worked with Tekashi. Read the comments below. Also read: SAUTI SOL PUSHES OUT LAUNCH              